column5: Does anyone have any expierence fishing Wawang Lake.We are looking for a possible lake to fish in late June to early July. Thanks.
There is quite a bit of info if you do a search here on walleyecentral on Wawang Lake.
The posts on wawang lake were not good,but the last post was in 2003,does anyone have any recent updates, they may have changed? Their web site looks good but..... Thanks for any info. t-bird
